						<summary>

						<p>This has a short introduction beginning with the words <hi rend="italic">Būmiyum Tiruvum.</hi> It is damaged and also incomplete. It seems to register a sale of land by the assembly of Pēriṅgūr to the temple (for the expenses of worship) to god Pichchadēvar (Bhikshāṭana).</p>						

